data.description: Located in the popular neighborhood of Falcons Landing, this lovely 4 BDRM, 2.5 BTHRM two-story is ready for its new owners. Well-maintained landscaping and a stately brick exterior welcome you as you move toward the covered front entrance. Once inside you are greeted with a spacious open floor plan that features high ceilings and ample natural light. Truly an ideal layout for entertaining, relaxing, hosting, you name it! The first living area seamlessly connects to the main living space, which then flows into the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen boasts upgraded gray cabinetry, white granite countertops, modern stainless steel appliances, decorative tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry, and an eye-catching oversized island w/ storage and an overhang for additional seating. On the second floor, you'll find another living space, with all bedrooms, and a guest bath. You'll have no trouble relaxing in the generously sized primary suite, which includes a private ensuite bathroom complete with a dual sink vanity, soaking tub, separate walk-in shower, and a large walk-in closet. Pride of ownership shows both inside and outside--An extended back patio slab offers additional outdoor living space where you can enjoy the flowering trees and tastefully done landscaping. Homeowners in this neighborhood have access to first-rate amenities such as a playground, pool, and walking trails. With easy access to major thoroughfares, shopping, restaurants, and more, you'll want to schedule your showing ASAP.    Home does have a Solar Panel and water softener system.
